When I asked the manager to help with the cab fare, she shrugged and said "no, we can't do that".	I feel like they are missing a trick as I would have paid for some help with bookings and recommendations.	When I was checking in the receptionist provided us with a clear street map and highlighted where to visit and how best to get there which was a great help.	I wouldn't choose to stay here again, the phone signal issue is just too irritating.	Never hesitated to help us and they were never rude compared to a lot of restaurants around Rome.